Implemented Apple Maps POI search + location data model for Over the Horizon iOS app. All requirements complete: LocationCategory enum (24 types, no restaurants), POILocation model (name, coordinate, category, distance, bearing, prominence), POISearchManager with MKLocalSearch, configurable radius (1-10 mi, default 5), periodic re-search on 500m movement. 32 comprehensive tests, all Swift files parse successfully, no syntax errors.
